room_title: Escape room "Race for the Deed" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
room_description: Aunt Ruth was nobody’s favorite relative. Forgetful at best and downright cruel at worst, Ruth has finally passed on to the hereafter (thank goodness). All that’s left is her memorial service and the reading of her will – but Ruth has one more trick up her sleeve. Will she leave her estate to the heirs that show up to her service – or will she ensure that everybody joins her in the afterlife?
